# M1: Core Systems Implementation Plan

**Design:** [docs/designs/2026-03-01-m1-core-systems.md](../designs/2026-03-01-m1-core-systems.md)

**Goal:** Full economy simulation (buy/repair/sell + warranties + legal cascade + loans + REP) playable via button dashboard UI.

**Architecture:** MonoBehaviour singleton stack with plain C# data classes. All logic testable in EditMode (no Play mode needed for core systems).

**EC Context:**
- Decision #78: MonoBehaviour singleton stack, domain managers, POCO data layer
- Decision #79: Throwaway playtest dashboard, uGUI
- Decision #80: BalancingConfig ScriptableObject with live debug sliders
- Decision #81: Unity 6, URP 2D, .NET 10, feature/ branch convention

**Test command:** Unity Test Runner EditMode — tests live in `DWD/Assets/Tests/EditMode/`

---

